metadata.name: Glitch Witch - Blue Glitch
metadata.description: The Glitch Witch has unleashed myriad glitches, infiltrating our very bones. Seize this opportunity, as collectors can now acquire this OE. Be sure to grab a few, enabling you to indulge in exchanging these pieces for an array of captivating variations that will surely appease your relentless glitch itch. Brought to you by Heytvm & Nah Fungible Bones!
